snowline
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a high country area above which sheep are not grazed in safety except in mid-summer.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
